§ API
COMMAND ┬ token ─ TOKEN
        └╥ Get_devs ↪ UUID ↦ DEV
         ╟ Change_dev ┬ uuid ─ UUID
         ║            └ dev ─ DEV  all fields optional, also "delete:true" to del; also allows for token,R_SSID,R_PASS
         ╟ Set_scene ┬ uuids ─ *UUID  ← remove this field once we have proper DB storage of user scenes?
         ║           └ scene ─ SCENE_ACTIVATION
         ║           ↪ *𝔹
         ╟ Del_scene ┬ uuids ─ *UUID
         ║           └ scene ─ NAME
         ║           ↪ *𝔹  if the scene existed prior
         ╟ Push_scenes ┬ uuids ─ *UUID
         ║             └ scenes ─ NAME ↦ SCENE
         ║             ↪ *ℕ  number of sucessfully saved scenes
         ╟ Pull_scenes ─ uuids ─ *UUID
         ║             ↪ *(NAME ↦ SCENE)
         ╟ Set_schedule ┬ uuids ─ *UUID  ← remove this field once we have proper DB storage of user scenes?
         ║              └ schedule ─ ℕ ↦ SCENE_ACTIVATION  key is seconds from UTC week start
         ╙ Pull_schedule ┬ uuids ─ *UUID
                         └ *(ℕ ↦ SCENE_ACTIVATION)
